'{"es":"Antiinflamatoria","en":"Anti-inflammatory","fr":"Anti-inflammatoire","it":"Antinfiammatoria"}',
'{"es":"Prioriza alimentos que reducen la inflamación sistémica. Especialmente útil en endometriosis, SOP, artritis y enfermedades autoinmunes.","en":"Prioritises foods that reduce systemic inflammation. Especially useful in endometriosis, PCOS, arthritis and autoimmune diseases.","fr":"Privilégie les aliments qui réduisent l''inflammation systémique. Particulièrement utile dans l''endométriose, le SOPK, l''arthrite.","it":"Privilegia gli alimenti che riducono l''infiammazione sistemica. Particolarmente utile nell''endometriosi, PCOS, artrite."}',
'{"es":["Pescado azul rico en omega-3 (salmón, sardinas, caballa)","Frutos rojos (arándanos, fresas, cerezas)","Cúrcuma y jengibre","Verduras de hoja verde (espinacas, kale)","Aceite de oliva virgen extra","Nueces y semillas de lino","Brócoli y crucíferas","Té verde"],"en":["Oily fish rich in omega-3 (salmon, sardines, mackerel)","Berries (blueberries, strawberries, cherries)","Turmeric and ginger","Dark leafy greens (spinach, kale)","Extra virgin olive oil","Walnuts and flaxseeds","Broccoli and cruciferous vegetables","Green tea"],"fr":["Poissons gras riches en oméga-3 (saumon, sardines, maquereau)","Fruits rouges (myrtilles, fraises, cerises)","Curcuma et gingembre","Légumes à feuilles vertes (épinards, kale)","Huile d''olive vierge extra","Noix et graines de lin","Brocoli et crucifères","Thé vert"],"it":["Pesce azzurro ricco di omega-3 (salmone, sardine, sgombro)","Frutti di bosco (mirtilli, fragole, ciliegie)","Curcuma e zenzero","Verdure a foglia verde (spinaci, kale)","Olio extravergine di oliva","Noci e semi di lino","Broccoli e crucifere","Tè verde"]}',
'{"es":["Azúcar refinado","Aceites vegetales refinados (maíz, girasol, soja)","Carnes rojas y procesadas","Alcohol","Ultraprocesados","Trans fats","Gluten (en casos de sensibilidad)","Lácteos convencionales (en algunos casos)"],"en":["Refined sugar","Refined vegetable oils (corn, sunflower, soy)","Red and processed meats","Alcohol","Ultra-processed foods","Trans fats","Gluten (in sensitivity cases)","Conventional dairy (in some cases)"],"fr":["Sucre raffiné","Huiles végétales raffinées (maïs, tournesol, soja)","Viandes rouges et transformées","Alcool","Ultra-transformés","Graisses trans","Gluten (en cas de sensibilité)","Produits laitiers conventionnels (dans certains cas)"],"it":["Zucchero raffinato","Oli vegetali raffinati (mais, girasole, soia)","Carni rosse e trasformate","Alcol","Ultra-processati","Grassi trans","Glutine (nei casi di sensibilità)","Latticini convenzionali (in alcuni casi)"]}',
